(938, 'Kimberly J. Brown', '1984-11-16', 'Lexington, Kentucky, U.S.', 1, 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cjowbswZrv8M3kmZ25Yv2Tg1UPC.jpg', 'From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.\n\nKimberly J. Brown (born Kimberly Jean Brown on November 16, 1984) Is an American actress. She is known for her role as Marah Lewis #3 on The Guiding Light and for her role as Marnie Piper on the Halloweentown series (1-3 only).\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Kimberly J. Brown, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.​'),
